== Overview ==
The Ion Flux Plus is the largest Ion reactor with over double the effectiveness of the standard [[Ion|Ion reactor]].

== Where to Acquire ==
The Ion Flux Plus Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

